      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "### Structural alerts relevant to hERG\n- **Large, lipophilic, polyaromatic scaffold** (common in hERG binders)\n- **Amide-linked aryl \u201cterfenadine-like\u201d hydrophobe pattern** (hydrophobic slabs + a central heteroatom region)\n- **But:** lacks a **clearly cationic/basic center** (classic high-risk feature)",
